com.orientechnologies.orient.core.index

Class OIndexChangesWrapper

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.orientechnologies.orient.core.index.OIndexChangesWrapper
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    OIndexCursor, Iterator<OIdentifiable>

    public class OIndexChangesWrapper
extends Object
implements OIndexCursor
    Wrapper which is used to detect whether the cursor is working with index which is being rebuilt at the moment.

    If such situation is detected any call to any method throws OIndexIsRebuildingException

    See Also:
    OIndexAbstract.getRebuildVersion()
